headline: Keysight Collaborates on Airbus UpNext SpaceRAN Demonstrator to Advance 5G NTN Innovation
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., January 20, 2026--Keysight provides advanced emulation solutions to support ground testing of 5G non-terrestrial network capabilities.
